                    <span>2015-11-02</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">Forever sniper……</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1043070796">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1043070796" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1043070796" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1043070796">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/119568026/">完蛋了的国王</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-06-20</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">十杆足以改变美国历史的枪，也足以体现美国枪械制造业的强大。纪念凯尔，他不仅是名留青史的好枪手，也有令人侧目的好文笔。美中不足的倒是本书糟糕的校对。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

